column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/6c1bf199ca25809b0e6323a4dcbe5be97ce84cd9 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
I suppose this should be "Bitcoin Core developers" now. I don't like change the world commits, but for new license messages we may as well do so.\n
